{"data":[{"date":"15:55 17/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ... mua d\u00ea","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/doi-bong-tho-nhi-ky-ban-cau-thu-de-mua-de.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0 Gulspor quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i d\u00ea nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o ngu\u1ed3n thu nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 trang tr\u1ea3i chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o.</h2>Gulspor b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y kho\u1ea3ng 2.600 \u0111\u00f4la. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 10 con d\u00ea.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i, Gulspor s\u1ebd b\u00e1n s\u1eefa v\u00e0 th\u1ecbt. N\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ebfn 140 con trong v\u00f2ng s\u00e1u n\u0103m.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3  mua d\u00ea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3  mua d\u00ea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/kenan2-9427-1534478287.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 trang tr\u1ea1i d\u00ea m\u1edbi l\u1eadp n\u00ean. \u1ea2nh: Haber7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Gulspor, Kenan Buyuklelbleb chia s\u1ebb h\u00f4m 15/8: ''\u0110\u00e0n d\u00ea s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n thu nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t th\u1ecbt v\u00e0 s\u1eefa. Hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00ea s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean 140 con v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2024''.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1ec1 l\u00fd do ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i, Kenan gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch: ''Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 150 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Ch\u00fang th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng CLB chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu n\u00e0o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n thu nh\u1eadp li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trong khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 hay c\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0o''. <br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5596","checkdouble":"194679"},{"date":"16:02 17/08","title":"Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/anh-trai-messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> B\u00e1o Argentina \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t loan tin Matias Messi, anh trai c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, b\u1ecb k\u1ebft \u00e1n t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u1edd La Capital \u0111\u01b0a tin anh trai Messi b\u1ecb c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t b\u1eaft gi\u1eef v\u00ec t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p. Matias b\u1ecb k\u1ebft \u00e1n 2 n\u0103m t\u00f9, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00e1n treo. Trong v\u00f2ng 2 n\u0103m, anh ph\u1ea3i lao \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f4ng \u00edch v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tham gia ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anh trai Messi \u0111i t\u00f9 v\u00ec t\u1ed9i t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef v\u0169 kh\u00ed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/Anh-trai-Messi-di-tu-vi-toi-tang-tru-vu-khi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Matias \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n chi\u1ebfc cano d\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00e1u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a Matias b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 12/2017. Anh trai Messi b\u1ecb b\u1eaft khi c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea9u s\u00fang mang d\u1ea5u v\u00e2n tay c\u1ee7a anh ta tr\u00ean cano d\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ebft m\u00e1u. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ecb b\u1eaft, Matias \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ee9t x\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0m m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 d\u1eadp s\u1ed1ng m\u0169i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng Jorge Horacio Messi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 con trai m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u00f9ng v\u0169 kh\u00ed cho cu\u1ed9c thanh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1eabm m\u00e1u nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi. Sau th\u1eddi gian \u0111i\u1ec1u tra, c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn Matias ch\u1ec9 t\u00e0ng tr\u1eef s\u00fang tr\u00e1i ph\u00e9p n\u00ean ph\u1ea1t anh 2 n\u0103m t\u00f9 giam. N\u1ebfu b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u00fang, Matias c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u00e1n t\u00f9 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 8,5 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong gia \u0111\u00ecnh Messi, Matias l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u tai ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t. Matias r\u1ea5t \u0111am m\u00ea s\u00fang \u0111\u1ea1n, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c. Th\u1eddi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb, Matias t\u1eebng b\u1ecb c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t b\u1eaft v\u00ec t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed9m c\u01b0\u1edbp v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh hung ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. Sau n\u00e0y, Matias hay qua l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i \u0111en.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gia dinh Messi lien tuc gap rac roi trong nhung nam gan day.\" title=\"Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/1_63251.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00f2ng ba n\u0103m, th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean gia \u0111\u00ecnh Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan lu\u1eadt ph\u00e1p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u00f4ng Jorge g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn v\u00ec t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi b\u1ecb t\u00f2a \u00e1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha k\u1ebft \u00e1n 21 th\u00e1ng t\u00f9. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh c\u1ea3nh ng\u1ed3i sau song s\u1eaft, h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 7/2017, si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Barcelona ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p ph\u1ea1t h\u01a1n 250.000 euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p h\u01a1n 150.000 euro \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb ng\u1ed3i t\u00f9 18 th\u00e1ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai cha con Messi ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i 4,1 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u01a1 quan thu\u1ebf T\u00e2y Ban Nha (bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u00e3i).</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5595","checkdouble":"194681"},{"date":"16:05 17/08","title":"Kh\u00f4ng l\u1ed9 th\u00e2n ph\u1eadn, con trai Ronaldinho v\u1eabn g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/khong-lo-than-phan-con-trai-ronaldinho-van-gay-an-tuong-voi-tuyen-trach-vien.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5594","checkdouble":"194682"},{"date":"16:07 17/08","title":"Griezmann ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u Ramos sau danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/17/griezmann-che-gieu-ramos-sau-danh-hieu-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u0103ng quang Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f9ng Atletico Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e2m ch\u1ecdc trung v\u1ec7 Sergio Ramos.</h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh song kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, chung cu\u1ed9c Atletico v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/griezmann.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111o\u1ea1t c\u00fap, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Instagram \u0103n m\u1eebng. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn ra nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 World Cup c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ch\u00e2m ch\u1ecdc trung v\u1ec7 Ramos. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean, Griezmann s\u1eafm vai v\u1ecb vua ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean ngai v\u00e0ng, c\u00f2n Ramos tr\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ee9ng sau \u0111\u1ed9i m\u0169 cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i. H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3t y\u00eau th\u00edch t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Griezmann th\u1ef1c ra c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi Atletico c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Champions League 2013/14 v\u00e0 2015/16.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5593","checkdouble":"194683"},{"date":"15:41 17/08","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt c\u00f2n \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn.\r\n\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Olympic Tolyo 2020 khi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c '\u0111\u00e0n em' \u00edt tu\u1ed5i, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng&nbsp;th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo&nbsp;c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt non kinh nghi\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt non kinh nghi\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/Duong-vu-Lam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o VOV: <em>&quot;Hai tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, ch\u00fang ta g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 50/50.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kinh nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang ta, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. C\u00e1c em trong \u0111\u1ed9i U21 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i CLB J-League 1 v\u00e0 J-League 2.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mang l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y sang ASIAD 2018 v\u00ec h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Olympic 2020 di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Tokyo. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u 2020 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd&quot;.<br>\r\n</em></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng L\u00e2m ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00eam: &quot;<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 b\u0103ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt quay l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Nepal. Trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 r\u00f5 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. Khi Nepal &quot;d\u1ef1ng xe bus&quot; tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh th\u00ec c\u00e1c em tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i, non kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao tr\u1eadn m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Olympic Pakistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edf th\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u1eb1m \u1edf kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb n\u00ean ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft \u1ee9ng ph\u00f3 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 l\u00f9i s\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t&quot;.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m cho r\u1eb1ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111i s\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf ASIAD n\u0103m nay. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-vs-nhat-ban-buoc-phai-thang-chua-han-la-dieu-xau-292-194668.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Quang H\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5592","checkdouble":"194677"},{"date":"16:22 17/08","title":"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u01a1i t\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed su\u00fdt thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Bangladesh.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bao Thai Lan khen Olympic Viet Nam sau man trinh dien khong tot cua doi tuyen nuoc nay.\" title=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh t\u00edch tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. T\u1edd Khaosod vi\u1ebft: &quot;L\u1ee9a U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i sau khi \u0111o\u1ea1t HCV SEA Games 29, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o qua hai tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb ch\u00ea t\u01a1i t\u1ea3<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang b\u1ecb thu h\u1eb9p khi h\u1ecd m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Uzbekistan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. N\u1ebfu thua tr\u1eadn, Th\u00e1i Lan nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong vi\u1ec7c so th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n&quot; l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean SiamSport. T\u1edd n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi ch\u00ea th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot: &quot;L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n, thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Bangladesh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng HLV Worrawoot ch\u1eb3ng th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;S\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn xa, \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi Chenrop Samphaodi \u0111ang sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9&quot;.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-lang-tranh-truyen-thong-que-nha-sau-tran-thang-nepal-168-194673.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ea3ng tr\u00e1nh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bat-dong-noi-bo-olympic-nepal-da-tu-thua-viet-nam-ngay-truoc-tran-472-194637.html\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, Olympic Nepal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-gap-nhat-ban-khi-chien-thang-khong-con-qua-xa-xi-168-194634.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa x\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-tinh-toan-nhieu-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194633.html\">&ldquo;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eebng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5591","checkdouble":"194680"},{"date":"16:10 17/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\r\n\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng D t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: <em>\"T\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tranh ch\u1ea5p ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. T\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t\".</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HLV Park Hang-seo v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n n\u00e9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E l\u00e0 Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Park n\u00f3i th\u00eam: <em>\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay b\u1ea5t k\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd c\u0103ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\".</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\"T\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m h\u1ebft tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam\",</em> v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt c\u00f2n \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Quang H\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5590","checkdouble":"194684"},{"date":"17:11 17/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/14/van-quyet-the-hien-su-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-thang-nepal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Paksitan, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Nepal m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat t\u1ea1i Wibawa Mukti t\u1ed1i qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt do h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 fair-play.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/video-ban-thang-van-quyet-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-pakistan.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u1edbi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng sau. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nepal, khi \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cTo\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 so \u0111\u1ecd hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Nepal ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra nh\u01b0ng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u1eabn nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh\u00a0 anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9: \u201cOlympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 cho m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean t\u00f4i xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 sang t\u1eadn Indonesia c\u1ed5 v\u0169 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i vui v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i Nepal, mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi.\u00a0\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194685.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194685.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 Messi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br>\r\nM\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1eb7t cho c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1 m\u0129 mi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 Messi Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194684.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194684.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta-292-194680.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta-292-194680.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u01a1i t\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt c\u00f2n \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5589","checkdouble":"194686"},{"date":"14:37 17/08","title":"Sao Man City tham v\u1ecdng th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh d\u00e0i l\u00e2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/16/Danh-sach-nhung-cau-thu-choi-tot-nhat-vong-27-Premier-League-hinh-anh-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kyle Walker hay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i chung c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp, Manchester City quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u00edt nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u1edf chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League 2018/19 n\u0103m nay, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 tham v\u1ecdng l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Champions League.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kyle Walker t\u1ef1 tin Man City b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kyle Walker t\u1ef1 tin Man City b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/16/Danh-sach-nhung-cau-thu-choi-tot-nhat-vong-27-Premier-League-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kyle Walker quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f9ng Man City b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">\u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Kyle Walker t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed trong c\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo sau \u0111\u00e2y. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh: \u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Pep Guardiola kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Man City mu\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 cao t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea1i g\u00ec, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f2n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh d\u00e0i d\u00e0i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 HLV t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. \u0110\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng, kh\u00e1t khao kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t h\u01a1n. Nh\u00ecn xem, ngay c\u1ea3 Everton c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh tay tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man City s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Huddersfield Town. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh Arsenal ngay t\u1ea1i Emirates.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-pep-team-khong-ngu-quen-tren-chien-thang-172-194353.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-pep-team-khong-ngu-quen-tren-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-pep-team-khong-ngu-quen-tren-chien-thang-172-194353.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: \u201cPep Team\u201d kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ee7 qu\u00ean tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Arsenal kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Man City c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n....</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5588","checkdouble":"194669"},{"date":"14:56 17/08","title":"Emery kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0103n g\u1ea1ch sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/emery-khong-ngung-an-gach-sau-that-bai-cua-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Martin Keown l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac trong th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda khi Arsenal nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i hai b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110KV\u0110 Man City ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1eadn thua Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1eadn thua Arsenal 0-2 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/emery-khong-ngung-an-gach-sau-that-bai-cua-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1eadn thua Arsenal 0-2 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Theo \u0111\u00f3 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c t\u00e2n binh Bernd Leno ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Petr Cech, Lucas Torreira c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u trung v\u1ec7 Martin Keown l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Emery v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i: \u201cArsenal d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cH\u00e0ng n\u0103m tr\u1eddi qua, c\u00e1c C\u0110V ch\u1ec9 mong ng\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Th\u1ebf m\u00e0 r\u1ed3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Man City, \u00f4ng ta xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng hai n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Guendouzi, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c Emery \u0111ang \u0111i theo l\u1ed1i m\u00f2n c\u1ee7a Arsene Wenger trong c\u00e1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Torreira s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5587","checkdouble":"194670"},{"date":"15:44 17/08","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong nh\u00f3m \"h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\" s\u1eafp b\u1ecb Liverpool thanh l\u00fd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/liverpool-sap-ban-ragnar-klavan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng di\u1ec5n ra, Ragnar Klavan s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Liverpool trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal \u0111\u01b0a tin, Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan cho Cagliari v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (2.5 tri\u1ec7u euro). Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Estonia s\u1ebd bay sang Italia trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ebb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Cagliari.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/liverpool-sap-ban-ragnar-klavan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan cho Cagliari.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRagnar Klavan gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool n\u0103m 2016, ra s\u00e2n 53 tr\u1eadn sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Van Dijk, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Joe Gomez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 khi\u1ebfn HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n Klavan n\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Jurgen Klopp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 hai trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Dejan Lovren v\u00e0 Joel Matip.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 b\u1edfi trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n mua Klavan nh\u01b0ng Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool thanh l\u00fd h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ragnar Klavan, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c ra \u0111i l\u00e0 Danny Ward, Jon Flanagan v\u00e0 Emre Can. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Kop v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong di\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 Simon Mignolet, Lazar Markovic, Pedro Chirivella, Marko Grujic v\u00e0 Divock Origi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi h\u01a1n 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed1n t\u00e2n binh, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tay HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u1ea3 ba tuy\u1ebfn. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Liverpool \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ra \u0111i v\u1eeba thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed, v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho HLV Jurgen Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League g\u1eb7p West Ham, Liverpool gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-roi-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-194419.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-tu-choi-ban-hang-thai-cho-newcastle-172-194271.html\">HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i cho Newcastle</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ghi-ban-phut-bu-gio-klavan-di-vao-lich-su-premier-league-172-176760.html\">Ghi b\u00e0n ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, sao Liverpool \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed NHA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-liverpool-to-salah-tron-tap-luyen-172-173564.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1 Salah tr\u1ed1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-liverpool-len-tieng-thach-thuc-sergio-aguero-172-156173.html\">Sao Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Sergio Aguero</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klavan-su-canh-tranh-vi-tri-la-tot-cho-liverpool-172-139137.html\">Klavan: S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5586","checkdouble":"194675"},{"date":"17:27 17/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/day-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby London.</h2><h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Cesc Fabregas. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFabregas kh\u00f3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Anh g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a The Blues \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a The Blues h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a The Blues h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/172219-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Fabregas</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hai b\u00ean k\u00fd k\u1ebft c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Huddersfield cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMarco van Ginkel \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf PSV. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng ch\u1eef th\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Chelsea\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh Chelsea\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/3.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nChelsea s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng 4-3-3 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEden Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t sau khi ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u1ed3i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf Willian. Pedro \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Sarri trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea (4-3-3): Kepa &ndash; Azpilicueta, Luiz, Rudiger, Alonso &ndash; Kante, Jorginho, Barkley &ndash; Pedro, Morata, Hazard<br>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn</h2>\r\n- Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 5 trong 6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 thua Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n. H\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd thua 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1992<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Th\u1eddi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, HLV Sarri ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 4 trong s\u1ed1 57 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 (th\u1eafng 43, h\u00f2a 10)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Olivier Giroud \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n cho Arsenal khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2/2017. N\u1ebfu ghi b\u00e0n cho Chelsea, anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 2 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i sau Cesc Fabregas<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 150 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf 5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB&nbsp;Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-bom-tan-cua-chelsea-het-loi-172-194639.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-hlv-sarri-giua-hai-nga-barkley-kovacic-172-194552.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Sarri gi\u1eefa hai ng\u1ea3 Kovacic - Barkley</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5585","checkdouble":"194687"},{"date":"17:45 17/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Morata l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/17/huyen-thoai-bay-cach-giup-morata-lay-lai-kha-nang-san-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Dennis Wise tin r\u1eb1ng Morata c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 s\u0103n b\u00e0n nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Gianfranco Zola.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Morata m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong n\u0103m 2018. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Chelsea sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh T\u00e2y Ban Nha tham d\u1ef1 World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0 HLV Sarri mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, Morata v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00e0y c\u00e1ch cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/huyen-thoai-bay-cach-giup-morata-lay-lai-kha-nang-san-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Dennis Wise cho r\u1eb1ng Zola c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Dennis Wise cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Gianfranco Zola c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Morata gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap Morata ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed9t khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi Premier League. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Morata. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb Zola. S\u1ebd th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu Zola c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 che ch\u1edf Morata v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. N\u1ebfu Morata ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Chelsea s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi Morata. Giroud ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed5 s\u00fang khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xung quanh Morata ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang h\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu \u0111i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5584","checkdouble":"194688"}]}